<div id="pf5" class="pf w0 h0" data-page-no="5"><div class="pc pc5 w0 h0"><img class="bi x0 y0 w1 h1" alt="" src="bg5.png"/><div class="t m61 x26 h15 y69 ff1 fsd fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Why Do </div><div class="t m62 x26 h15 y6a ff1 fsd fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Christians Give </div><div class="t m63 x26 h15 y6b ff1 fsd fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Offerings? </div><div class="t m64 x26 h16 y6c ff2 fse fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">111 To ensure God&apos;s continued protection? </div><div class="t m65 x26 h16 y6d ff2 fse fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">111 Because everyone is expected to give? </div><div class="t m42 x27 h17 y6e ff6 fse fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">‚ùë </div><div class="t m66 x28 h16 y6f ff2 fse fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">To appease one&apos;s conscience? </div><div class="t m67 x29 h18 y70 ff4 fsf fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">7 </div><div class="t m68 x29 h16 y71 ff2 fse fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">o </div><div class="t m69 x2a h16 y72 ff2 fse fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">express love and </div><div class="t m6a x2b h16 y73 ff2 fse fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">ratitude to God? </div><div class="t m6b x29 h18 y74 ff4 fsf fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">r </div><div class="t m68 x29 h16 y75 ff2 fse fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">o </div><div class="t m6c x2a h16 y76 ff2 fse fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">hasten the work </div><div class="t m6d x11 h16 y77 ff2 fse fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">of God in the earth? </div><div class="t m6e x27 h19 y78 ff1 fs10 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">No Other Way </div><div class="t m6f x2c h1a y79 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">&quot;The Lord does not need our </div><div class="t m70 x2d h1a y7a ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">offerings. We cannot enrich Him by </div><div class="t m71 x2d h1a y7b ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">our gifts. Says the psalmist, &quot;All </div><div class="t m72 x2d h1a y7c ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">thins come of thee, and of thine </div><div class="t m73 x2d h1a y7d ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">owave we given thee.&quot; </div><div class="t m2 x5 h1a y7d ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">&quot;Yet God </div><div class="t m74 x2d h1a y7e ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">permits us to show our appreciation </div><div class="t m75 x2d h1a y7f ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">of his mercies by self-sactific </div><div class="t m76 x2d h1a y80 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">efforts to extend the same to others. </div><div class="t m77 x2d h1a y81 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">This is the only way in which it is </div><div class="t m78 x2d h1a y82 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">possible for us to manifest our </div><div class="t m4 x27 h1a y83 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">gratitude and love to God. He </div><div class="t m79 x2d h1a y84 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">has provided no other way&quot; </div><div class="t m7a x2e h1b y85 ff3 fsc fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">(Review and Herald, </div><div class="t m7b x6 h1b y86 ff2 fsc fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Dec. 6. 1887). </div><div class="t m7c x1b h1c y87 ff7 fse fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Express your gratitude this quarter </div><div class="t m7d x1e h1c y88 ff7 fse fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">through systematic planned giving. </div></div><div class="pi" data-data='{"ctm":[1.000000,0.000000,0.000000,1.000000,0.000000,0.000000]}'></div></div>
